{"tid":2175766,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[tldr][純呻勿入]點樣喺個充滿壓力嘅環境下保持正能量？","createTime":"2020-08-26T16:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T01:50:23.000Z","uid":64601,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fad09b32b7c70a9695cd7ad65410ef809637dbcb","tid":2175766,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"呢排發生好多事，以為一件傷心事完咗，當你慢慢爬返上嚟嘅事候，原來懸崖邊等緊你嘅係接二連三嘅壓力。最近呀嫲起床冇力，我就日日放工送埋飯俾佢，呢兩日入院，仲要診斷埋有骨髓癌，醫生話做treatment會好辛苦，未必頂到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身有個垃圾大伯，完全靠唔撚住，幾廿歲人仲on99咁，佢哋亦似乎想唔做治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身間intern公司係首屈一指癌症製藥公司，點知喺呢個時候完全幫唔到手，覺得好無力。啫係同開咗倒數計時冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後到而家都未搵到grad job，本身已經遲人兩年，成日喺度俾壓力自己，點樣先追得返呢兩年，就算搵個同年嘅伴侶，都覺得呢刻嘅自己俾唔到未來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚟緊去銀行做個垃圾placement，本身ongoing嘅interview得兩個，但呢兩日收到三個call約interview，一個我reject咗，然後連續四個工作天見4份工。本身份intern做咗一年幾，好有感情，好多knowledge集中喺我身上，淨低呢4日我又要盡快將我嘅knowledge transfer俾啲staff，又擔心佢哋搞唔掂，教咗佢哋兩個月仲不時問我啲基本嘢，個intern我refer返嚟，佢又係靠唔住，我同vendor開meeting，佢事後話我知話有我喺度，所以冇點聽，我仲止意佢做到我successor<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住我知啲hr開始做嘢，又喺度擔心下個月返新placement，我點樣先可以完成啲interview，又驚要請假去interview俾壞印象人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己成日俾壓力自己，咩嘢都諗到好長遠，啫係拍拖我就會喺度諗對方如果30歲前結婚，我仲有幾多年時間可以努力，我每個月要儲幾多錢，幾時同居等等。如果要移民，我又要做咩工先可以達到技術移民水平，要點樣先俾到個安穩生活人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後慢慢亦開始好在意人情緒，有次我對住個intern講嘢rude咗啲，我夜晚whatsapp佢講sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我搵人講，講完都只係一剎那得到紓緩，冇人依靠到亦冇人可以幫到我，喺人面前自己搞下笑好活潑，但我嘅內心又可以點先保持開朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d059223107b3ba72f1281aecbd8aca7f8aa829af","tid":2175766,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"bfe2ea6baae1064df4a9c6fa8413963cd59efb01","tid":2175766,"uid":312193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"支持住呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd915d9df510f292f8512ed43606ed6018a2c98","tid":2175766,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d059223107b3ba72f1281aecbd8aca7f8aa829af","tid":2175766,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"0/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:10:29.000Z","msg":"我都覺得自己係零"},{"pid":"5ab8ba0f305e7b9034cbd6673f2991e228715b99","tid":2175766,"uid":165869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留個名 同你講句加油"},{"pid":"f1be3fa00f36019665e6bf88dab08b0ac343345a","tid":2175766,"uid":189911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"明白咗人生係不停loop,麻木咗就得，唔洗正能量"},{"pid":"3a99ecaeb81ebab55c06ef30e3da52cfd421bd34","tid":2175766,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"撐住呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新界北總區副指揮官曾正科交代及回應記者元朗721事件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fQBzmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fQBzmS</a>"},{"pid":"448c1f78120585b68ca27d38b1